<section class="framework">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="section-eyebrow">The Engage framework</div>
<h2>Five grids. One clear outcome.</h2>
<p class="lead">Every role assessed across five structured dimensions — consistently, transparently, with logic you can explain to any leader or employee.</p>
<div class="grid-cards">
<div class="grid-card"><div class="grid-num">01</div><h4>Technical</h4><p>Depth of knowledge required and how it is applied in practice.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card"><div class="grid-num">02</div><h4>Managerial</h4><p>Coordination and business decision-making authority.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card"><div class="grid-num">03</div><h4>Persuasive</h4><p>Influence — from general communication to commercial selling.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card"><div class="grid-num">04</div><h4>Control</h4><p>Staff reporting, sites controlled, and operational span.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card"><div class="grid-num">05</div><h4>Impact</h4><p>Organisational importance, accountability, and reporting context.</p></div>
</div>
